$ How to lie with statistics
by: Darrell Huff

Allegedly the most successful book on → science/mathematics/statistics.

"
  The secret language of statistics, so appealing in factminded culture,
  is empolyed to sensationalize, inflate, confuse, and oversimplify.
" [ p. 10 ]

